OL,3,CHistoric toll bridge reopens saving
OL,4,Cmotorist a 25-mile round trip
OL,6,FAn historic road bridge in North
OL,7,FYorkshire which has been closed for 10
OL,8,Fmonths has reopened, saving motorists
OL,9,Fa 25-mile round trip.
OL,11,FThe Grade II listed Aldwark toll
OL,12,Fbridge, which links villages either
OL,13,Fside of the River Ure in Easingworld,
OL,14,Fshut in April in order for it to
OL,15,Fundergo a #1m refurbishment.
OL,17,FIt is one of Yorkshire's last
OL,18,Fremaining private toll bridges and has
OL,19,Fbeen helping people across the water
OL,20,Ffor hundreds of years.
