OL,6,FDudley Valentine, the operations
OL,7,Fmanager for the bridge, told ITV News
OL,8,FCalendar: "It rattled very much, but
OL,9,Fyou go over it now and it's just like
OL,10,Fdriving over a normal highway now.
OL,12,F"The children aren't very happy about
OL,13,Fit because they like to come over the
OL,14,Frickety rackety bridge and it's not a
OL,15,Frickety rackety bridge anymore."
OL,17,FThe bridge dates back to the 1770s and
OL,18,Fis relied upon by hundreds of people
OL,19,Fevery day.
