OL,3,CHistoric toll bridge reopens saving
OL,4,Cmotorist a 25-mile round trip
OL,6,FIt was supposed to open in November
OL,7,Fbut it got delayed until Saturday 17
OL,8,FFebruary.
OL,10,FThe reopening comes as a huge boost to
OL,11,Flocal businesses and residents who've
OL,12,Fhad to cope with the detour while
OL,13,Frepair work was carried out.
OL,15,FJoanna Weatherill, who runs a
OL,16,Freflexology business opposite the toll
OL,17,Fbooth, said: "We've started to
OL,18,Freconnect with people on the other
OL,19,Fside of the bridge.
