OL,6,F"Just this morning I was at a coffee
OL,7,Fmorning at a local village, Linton.
OL,9,F"I've taken three bookings this
OL,10,Fmorning. It's massive - it's huge."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the Aldwark Arms pub saw
OL,13,Fits takings drop by 40% while the
OL,14,Fbridge was closed.
OL,16,FWarren Taylor, the landlord, told ITV
OL,17,FNews Calendar: "I'm very excited that
OL,18,Fit's back open and things are back to
OL,19,Fnormal.
